My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 45

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

The clock is ticking, the knives are out and the MKR doorbell is set to ring again. In a competition first, teams are heading back to home turf to battle it out in an ultimate instant restaurant round.
It's the final home restaurant - who will be eliminated?
